name: RTCIceCandidatePairStats.remoteCandidateId
description: The RTCIceCandidatePairStats property remoteCandidateId is a string that uniquely identifies the remote ICE candidate which was analyzed to generate the RTCIceCandidateStats used to compute the statistics for this pair of candidates.
